<DATE_TIME> 1997-12-12 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> URGENT: Eight Died in Helicopter Crash in Russia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, December 11 (Xinhua) -- At least eight people died and
five injured when a landing Russian military plane crashed into a
helicopter in the northern city of Naryan Mar on Thursday
afternoon, according to the Itar-Tass news agency.
</P>
<P>
A Mi-8 helicopter with 16 passengers on board had just landed
two minutes before an An-12 plane collided with it.
</P>
<P>
The Mi-8 helicopter was completely destroyed in the crash.
</P>
