atmosphere necessitates integration and cooperation among Arab
states.
</P>
<P>
He expressed the hope that in the course of their meetings
today and Friday, the two parties will reach agreements in the
economic, cultural, educational and other fields.
</P>
<P>
Asked about the most important agreements and protocols to be
concluded between Yemen and Egypt, Ganzouri said the overall
framework is that of consolidating bilateral economic ties on the
volume of trade and the size of joint investment, as well as the
removal of certain existing barriers in trade and
investment. 
