saying it was a sound foundation for a global cooperative
strategy.
</P>
<P>
In a statement issued by the spokesman's office, Annan said the
Kyoto conference on climate change had taken a major step towards
the objective of limiting growth in greenhouse gas emission.
</P>
<P>
