provided opportunities for partnership between government and the
private sector, notably in transferring finance and technology for
sustainable development.
</P>
<P>
Annan stressed this was a sound foundation for a global
cooperative strategy which would bring together governments, civil
society and the business community in a joint effort to protect a
common environmental resource.
</P>
<P>
He urged governments now to move expeditiously in ratifying and
implementing this historic agreement. 
