sometime in the second half of 1998, calendar year 1998," Bacon
added.
</P>
<P>
However, he said that while the anti-personnel landmines are
being picked up, there will remain in the mine field anti-tank
landmines to protect the naval base from action by the Cubans.
</P>
<P>
"Our mine field on the American side has been fenced in and
clearly designated a mine field in both English and Spanish,"
Bacon added. 
