was the biggest loser as it declined by 3.7 dollars to end at 28.9
Singapore dollars. Elec fell by 80 cents to close at 4.5 U.S.
dollars while the Singapore Press Holdings (SPH) Foreign lost 70
cents to finish at 20.5 Singapore dollars.  
