<HEADLINE> Turkish Woman Snatchs World Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CHIANG MAI, THAILAND, December 12 (Xinhua) -- Aysel Ozgur of
Turkey set a snatch world record in the women's 76-kilogram class
at the World Weightlifting Championships here on Friday.
