<HEADLINE> 6 Killed in Fire in Philippines </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, December 12 (Xinhua) -- A fire broke out in a house in
the northern Manila suburb of Quezon City early today, killing six
people sleeping inside, a fire officer said.
</P>
<P>
