<HEADLINE> Hungary, Czech Republic and Poland to Link Countries </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUDAPEST, December 11 (Xinhua) -- Hungary, the Czech Republic
and Poland decided Thursday to build a road linking the three
countries in efforts to join the European Union.
</P>
